		<title>「プラットフォームとフェデレーションとの競争」</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://text.baldanders.info/remark/2022/11/new-spark-of-competition-between-platforms-and-federations/" />
		<id>tag:text.Baldanders.info,2022-11-25:/remark/2022/11/new-spark-of-competition-between-platforms-and-federations/</id>
